getPartialNumber

public String getPartialNumber()
Returns:
A displayable partial number for the credit card that contains 10 astrixes and the last 4 digits from the card.

getSvn

public String getSvn()
A transient value for the security verification number on the back of the card. This is transient in the fact that it cannot be persited via JPA. It can however be serialized.

Returns:
The SVN.

getExpirationDate

public YearMonthDay getExpirationDate()
Returns:
A YearMonthDay that is the expiration date. This uses the last day of the month since most credit cards expire on the last day of the month.
